  ('social-worker-moex-08240', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依我國志願服務法第15條規定，下列那項行為是志工必須遵守之義務？', '["不能參加宗教活動", "不能接受機構安排的訓練", "不能接受服務運用單位之車馬費", "拒絕向受服務者收取報酬"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08241', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依我國志願服務法第16條規定，下列那個項目是志願服務運用單位應該要辦理的工作？', '["補助志工交通費", "補助志工誤餐費", "意外事故保險", "免費健康檢查"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08242', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一種人力資源管理工作側重於組織未來的工作取向，較著重於教育而非訓練，它灌輸員工正確的推理程序，增 進其理解和詮釋知識的能力而非只是特定的技術學習：', '["招募", "甄選", "員工培訓", "員工發展"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08243', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '讓員工能夠協調工作時間表與個人生活需求，而員工仍然被要求做滿一定的工作時數，但他們能夠在雇主所限定的工 作時段內選擇上班與下班的時點的選擇性工作調配制度稱為：', '["輪班制度", "彈性工時制度", "工作分擔制度", "電傳工作制度"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08244', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據Herzberg（1966）的雙因子理論，下列那一項因素能夠激勵員工努力工作，改善工作績效：', '["工作條件", "薪水", "成就感", "管理監督方式"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08245', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '機構雇主提供諮詢服務給員工，幫助他們解決一些問題如家庭問題、藥物或酒精濫用的員工福利服務稱為員工協助計 畫，其英文簡稱為：', '["EGG", "NPO", "NGO", "EAP"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08246', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '機構必須由一無所有開始，且機構必須為其每年所做的財務要求做辯護的預算類型稱為：', '["逐項預算", "功能式預算", "方案預算", "零基預算"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08247', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依我國公益勸募條例第12條規定，勸募團體辦理勸募活動期間，最長為：', '["三個月", "半年", "一年", "兩年"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08248', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關社會福利機構的財務管理的敘述，何者是正確的？', '["現在流行使用者付費的概念，因此募款對機構是不重要的", "只要好好依賴政府，機構就能活得好好的不用憂愁", "社會福利機構並非營利機構，因此並不需做財務管理", "機構對某一財源依賴度越高，越受其左右，因此機構應努力開拓其他財源"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-08249', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-098-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Ries與Trout（1993）認為有22個永恆不變的行銷法則值得注意，其中一個法則認為：「與其成為第一個進入市場的 品牌不如成為第一個消費者腦海中的品牌」，這個適用於非營利機構的行銷法則稱為：', '["領先法則", "類別法則", "心智法則", "焦點法則"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd967293a7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "822b4e781d88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098160", "c": "902", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年專技高考律師、會計師、社工師、不動產估價師、專利師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
